nodes.text: Deluxe nutmeat and jelly sandwich was a type of sandwich served in Dex's Diner on the planet Coruscant. Costing 4.5 credits, it was prepared with freshly ground ettel nuts and gourmet Andorian jelly and served on bleached Pseudograin bread. According to Dexter Jettster, it was a childhood favorite among many patrons.
